. Photographs of live 
<taxonomicName id="27CF4D65A706D66A78CD6886DDE145F6" authority="Satkunanathan &amp; Benjamin, 2022" authorityName="Satkunanathan &amp; Benjamin" authorityYear="2022" box="[509,721,1963,1989]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Carrhotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="88" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="atratus" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="D2BBEAF4A706D66A78CD6886DDE145F6" box="[509,721,1963,1989]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="88">Carrhotus atratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="C988578FA706D66A7BE86886DC0445F7" box="[728,820,1963,1989]" pageId="10" pageNumber="88" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
<emphasis id="D2BBEAF4A706D66A7A0D6887DC4345F6" bold="true" box="[829,883,1962,1988]" pageId="10" pageNumber="88">A–B</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="D2BBEAF4A706D66A7AB36886DC8645F7" bold="true" box="[899,950,1963,1989]" pageId="10" pageNumber="88">E–F</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="D2BBEAF4A706D66A7AF76886DCE245F7" bold="true" box="[967,978,1963,1989]" pageId="10" pageNumber="88">I</emphasis>
. Males. 
<emphasis id="D2BBEAF4A706D66A7D0A6887DB4245F6" bold="true" box="[1082,1138,1962,1988]" pageId="10" pageNumber="88">C–D</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="D2BBEAF4A706D66A7DB26887DB8E45F6" bold="true" box="[1154,1214,1962,1988]" pageId="10" pageNumber="88">G–H</emphasis>
. Females. A–H from Mandaitivu, I from Hiyare.
</paragraph>
