<subSubSection id="A8D5656DA702D66E798D6D35DBA240B7" pageId="14" pageNumber="92" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="E07036E6A702D66E798D6D35DEDE4000" blockId="14.[189,494,536,563]" box="[189,494,536,563]" pageId="14" pageNumber="92">
<heading id="BB38818AA702D66E798D6D35DEDE4000" bold="true" box="[189,494,536,563]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="14" pageNumber="92" reason="3">
<emphasis id="D2BBEAF4A702D66E798D6D35DEDE4000" bold="true" box="[189,494,536,563]" pageId="14" pageNumber="92">Distribution and habitat</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E07036E6A702D66E798D6D6ADBA240B7" blockId="14.[189,1398,583,645]" pageId="14" pageNumber="92">
This species occurs in the mangrove forest, in the arid zone and lowland secondary rainforest of 
<collectingCountry id="98D87676A702D66E7C646D6ADE3640B6" name="Sri Lanka" pageId="14" pageNumber="92">Sri Lanka</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation id="78F42A63A702D66E78266D47DE5D40B6" box="[278,365,618,644]" captionStart="Fig 17" captionStartId="28.[189,230,1982,2008]" captionTargetBox="[189,1382,719,1923]" captionTargetId="figure-115@28.[189,1397,718,1944]" captionTargetPageId="28" captionText="Fig 17. Distribution of Carrhotus spp. of Sri Lanka." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6518352" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6518352/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="92">Fig. 17</figureCitation>
). Specimens were collected by beating foliage up to a height of 
<specimenCount id="F6C9FD6FA702D66E7D6E6D47DBA240B7" box="[1118,1170,618,645]" pageId="14" pageNumber="92" type="generic">
<quantity id="27379B03A702D66E7D6E6D47DBBE40B7" box="[1118,1166,618,645]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="14" pageNumber="92" unit="m" value="2.0">2 m</quantity>
.
</specimenCount>
</paragraph>
